OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmainly dry but rather cloudy evening
OL,7,Fand night, with just the odd spot of
OL,8,Flight rain or drizzle possible at
OL,9,Ffirst.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA dry but fairly cloudy
OL,12,Fmorning. Cloud will partly break up
OL,13,Fthrough the afternoon, allowing some
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells to develop,
OL,15,Fespecially across northern
OL,16,FAberdeenshire and Moray.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
