OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand warm on Thursday with sunny
OL,7,Fspells, but cloudier, cooler east
OL,8,Fcoast at times. Variable cloud and
OL,9,Fbright spells on Friday. Dry start on
OL,10,FSaturday, rain later.
